sequenceDiagram
    box Browser
        actor User
        participant Client as React Client
    end
    box Next.js
        participant MW as Middleware
        participant API as /api/challenges/launch
        participant DB as SQLite
    end
    box Generation
        participant Gen as openrouter.ts
        participant OR as OpenRouter
    end
    box Infrastructure
        participant Ans as ansible-runner.ts
        participant Ver as verification-runner.ts
        participant PX as Proxmox / Ansible
    end

    User->>Client: Click "Launch Challenge"
    Client->>MW: POST /api/challenges/launch
    MW->>API: Forward (session validated)
    API->>DB: Check for active challenge
    DB-->>API: None found
    API-->>Client: SSE stream opened

    API-->>Client: progress: Generating vulnerability
    API->>Gen: generateVulnerability(category, difficulty, history)
    Gen->>OR: POST /v1/messages (json_schema)
    OR-->>Gen: VulnerabilitySpec JSON
    Gen->>Gen: Zod parse + policy validation
    Gen-->>API: spec + flag

    API-->>Client: progress: Deploying container
    API->>Ans: deployContainer(vmid)
    Ans->>PX: deploy.yml — pct create + start
    PX-->>Ans: vmid + ip
    Ans-->>API: vmid + ip

    API-->>Client: progress: Injecting vulnerability
    API->>Ans: injectVulnerability(vmid, spec, flag)
    Ans->>PX: inject-vulnerability.yml
    PX->>PX: Install packages, push files,\nset permissions, run setup, restart services
    PX-->>Ans: ok
    Ans-->>API: ok

    API-->>Client: progress: Verifying challenge
    API->>Ver: verifyInjectedChallenge(vmid, ip, flag, spec)
    Ver->>PX: verify-vulnerability.yml
    PX-->>Ver: JSON results
    Ver-->>API: VerificationResult

    alt Verification failed
        API->>Ans: destroyContainer(vmid)
        API-->>Client: error: verification failure detail
    else Verification passed
        API->>DB: INSERT challenge (status=active, expires_at=now+1h)
        DB-->>API: challenge record
        API-->>Client: complete: title · hint · SSH command
    end

    Client->>Client: Render challenge details
